\section{Introduction}
\textbf{Sachin Ramesh Tendulkar} is a former Indian cricketer and captain, widely regarded as one of the greatest batsmen of all time. He took cricket \index{cricket} at the age of eleven, made his Test \index{Test} debut \index{debut} on 15 November 1989 against Pakistan in Karachi at the age of sixteen. \cite{wiki}

